#### PR description:

This is a follow-up to https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/41787.
Miscellaneous improvements to the `DQM/TrackingMonitorSource` package left over from the previous PR:
   * merged plugin header files with implementations;
   * implemented `fillDescription` methods and used the auto-generated `cfi`-s in the corresponding configuration fragments;
   * general clean-up of unused includes;
   * code improvement where possible to conform with the `cmssw` standard;
   * implemented unit tests;

#### PR validation:

Relies on the unit tests introduced in this PR:
  * `cmssw` compiles
   * `scram b runtests` runs successfully

